  "texts": [
    "Categorization is not just, or even primarily, naming.",
    "It is doing (and learning to do) the right thing with the right kind (i.e., category) of thing.",
    "Identifying it by name comes late in the game.",
    "Nonhuman animals can and must learn to categorize too, and they never learn language (Makino et al. 2015).",
    "So do pre-verbal children, before they learn language (Gallistel 2016)."
